#: inc/class-astra-memory-limit-notice.php:298
msgid ""
"<strong>About PHP Memory:</strong> PHP memory limit determines how much "
"memory your website can use. Themes, plugins, and WordPress core all consume "
"memory. When the limit is reached, your site may display errors or stop "
"working."
